{"tid":32920,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"阿波羅全新嘅迷你韓國部隊鍋 $28 ！！","createTime":"2016-12-10T13:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T18:13:29.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c96dabdf330d8428d8c63935bd380c30a3555b3","tid":32920,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/6Ez2V9y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6Ez2V9y.jpg&h=5b6efce5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雪糕店都有熱食唔係好出奇&amp;#22021;，阿波羅一直都有賣燒賣、魚蛋、撈麵，不過最近趁天氣開始涼涼&amp;#21707;，推出全新&amp;#22021;迷你韓國部隊鍋。Poster 寫晒韓文，唔知味道又夠唔夠韓呢？<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/7KBcrgK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7KBcrgK.jpg&h=ac5c3e73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n迷你部隊鍋 $28（加 $4 配芬達橙汁或提子汁）<br />\n所謂部隊鍋，原來唔係用鍋載&amp;#22021;！可能係小食店關係，部隊鍋用紙碗載，方便捧住食。用辛辣麵，麵底即叫即煮。煮好麵條後，再倒入已放有辛辣麵調味粉&amp;#22021;碗內加湯拌勻，再放午餐肉、泡菜、茄汁豆及芝士，細細碗&amp;#22021;部隊鍋都幾多料喎！<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/lbea1KC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Flbea1KC.jpg&h=06ecd209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n迷你部隊鍋&amp;#22021;精髓之一，梗係午餐肉啦！不過呢碗部隊鍋&amp;#22021;午餐肉，有一塊係碎上。加上午餐肉無煎香過，吸引力大減！<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/EEZ1pjR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEEZ1pjR.jpg&h=e133a7a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有兩片車打芝士，放&amp;#21946;麵上受熱都有半融效果！好邪惡呀！<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cCrI9oQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcCrI9oQ.jpg&h=881b3b63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部隊鍋上面有 5、6 片泡菜，酸度剛好又唔太辣，質地爽脆。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Ro6qRoL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRo6qRoL.jpg&h=f8739104&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n茄汁豆&amp;#22021;分量就比較少，又無乜茄汁，拌勻都唔可以豐富部隊鍋湯底味道。提提想食&amp;#22021;朋友，迷你部隊鍋唔係所有分店都有得賣，只有設熱食檔&amp;#22021;分店先有&amp;#13774;！<br />\n<br />\n阿波羅 Appolo<br />\n地址：尚德商場地下 4 號舖<br />\n電話：2494 8881<br />\n營業時間：11am-9:30pm<br />\n註：部隊鍋於寶琳、華富、天澤、啟田、尚德、安定、沙角、禾輋等分店有售。"},{"pid":"1ae2ba2688c4a7d292c76aabcdfe1788b6821d4f","tid":32920,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:06:00.000Z","msg":"狗都唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96556bb677212a67f253f0838a2e6e98be302ac","tid":32920,"uid":21310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:06:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68a9642d80dc7d0c49f03f53e76d668b8eb025f1","tid":32920,"uid":9708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:06:54.000Z","msg":"改名叫部隊狗兜貼切d"},{"pid":"d6fb52a1b8e296cc91f40b79089b59717de35af0","tid":32920,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:08:02.000Z","msg":"嘔吐物<br />\n狗也不屌"},{"pid":"b8c413804cdbf0fe4e15f63cb429280b5c968599","tid":32920,"uid":36652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:08:48.000Z","msg":"好邪惡呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b16593020fb1c5f5af026268c97bc417b9712e3","tid":32920,"uid":62416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:13:14.000Z","msg":"鱔稿都影到pat屎咁 慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66e8b2badaebf003bf7eb9e74c9bf9fb3c3c280","tid":32920,"uid":26047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:15:07.000Z","msg":"攝影師已經盡晒力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41bdb8f1f124e350f89dd68f106201bc5d71deb8","tid":32920,"uid":5637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:17:25.000Z","msg":"真係狗都唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af233e4637e7ca228f24ef1ec62831312273de2a","tid":32920,"uid":57961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:20:22.000Z","msg":"賣垃圾都賣得咁落力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"